            <h2>YT-Shell</h2>
            <p class="date-label">APR/MAY 2021</p>
            <p class="type-label">Pure JS Chromium extension</p>
            <img alt="YT-Shell on www.youtube.com" src="pics/yt_shell_1.png" class="cover">
            <p>
                YT-Shell is a browser extension that helps you stay focused while browsing YouTube. The extension
                ensures that you are not distracted with the aim of spending your time on 'quality content'. It works by
                injecting CSS and JS that hide things from the site. There are settings for blocking stuff including
                blocking recommendations, hiding upcummies and thumbnails.
            </p>
